                    correct: 2,
                    explanation: "The /etc/rc.d directory (or similar locations) contains system startup and shutdown scripts that run at different runlevels."
                },
                {
                    question: "What command is used to kill processes?",
                    options: ["stop", "kill", "end", "terminate"],
